Hell-O
When you are looking for real underground hxc music, you listen to The Dillinger Escape Plan, Neglect, No Redeeming Social Value, Neck/Car^Bomb, Candiria, Murder City Devils, Sheer Terror/Joe Coffee, Gehenna (usa) , Integrity/Ringworm/In Cold Blood &...The Bad Luck 13 Riot Extravaganza.
"Bad Luck 13 Riot Extravaganza - Let the Riot Begin" (dvd) is very cool...
Hipsters can't understand the real deal 'cos their nightmares are just childhood monsters (= Heart-attack here).
